        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5672",
        "content": "But now, to speak in an Irish way, the crowd takes the platform, and looking down, sees itself swaying.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5672_88363_000002_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5672/88363/5672_88363_000002_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5672",
        "content": "Below the cliff caves were bar rooms in endless lines.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5672_88363_000002_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5672/88363/5672_88363_000002_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5672",
        "content": "There are almost as many bar rooms to day, yet this new thing breaks the lines as nothing else ever did.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5672_88363_000003_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5672/88363/5672_88363_000003_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5672",
        "content": "For no pious reason, surely.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5672_88363_000003_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5672/88363/5672_88363_000003_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5672",
        "content": "Now they have fire pouring into their eyes instead of into their bellies.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5672_88363_000003_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5672/88363/5672_88363_000003_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5672",
        "content": "Blood is drawn from the guts to the brain.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5672_88363_000003_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5672/88363/5672_88363_000003_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5672",
        "content": "After a day's work a street sweeper enters the place, heavy as King Log.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5672_88363_000004_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5672/88363/5672_88363_000004_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5672",
        "content": "The photoplays have done something to reunite the lower class families. No longer is the fire escape the only summer resort for big and little folks.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
